{
  "id": "adv_card_hrk_04_01",
  "title": "佐伯遙子 1話 羞恥心克服",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_04_01-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ……うふふ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hehe…uhu…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_04_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "遙子さん？\nやけに楽しそうですけど何かあったんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haruko-san?\nYou seem unusually happy. Did something happen?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_04_01-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "実はね、今から新しい衣装の試着をしに行くのよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ you know‚ I'm going to try on a new outfit now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_04_01-hrk003.m4a",
      "text": "新しい衣装ってわくわくするわよね\n今度はどんなデザインなのかしら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Trying on new outfits is so exciting‚ you know.\nI wonder what kind of design it is this time.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_04_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "そういえば今回の衣装制作は橋本さんに一任したから\n俺もまだ詳しくは聞けてなくて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "By the way‚ I left the outfit production entirely to Hashimoto-san this time.\nI haven't had a chance to ask for details yet…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_04_01-hrk004.m4a",
      "text": "さとみちゃんからは「あの衣装を遙子さんが着れば\n注目を集めること間違いなしです！」って言われたわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Satomi-chan told me‚\n\"If you wear that outfit‚ Haruko-san‚ it's sure to attract attention!\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_04_01-hrk005.m4a",
      "text": "新しい衣装で私の地味なイメージを\n一掃しちゃうんだから！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "With this new outfit‚\nI'll completely sweep away my plain image!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_04_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "別に遙子さんは地味ではないですよ……でも\n新衣装が気になるので俺も一緒に行っていいですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ Haruko-san‚ you're not plain at all… But\nI'm curious about the new outfit‚ so can I join you?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_04_01-hrk006.m4a",
      "text": "うん、ぜひ感想を聞かせてちょうだい\nうふふ……どんなデザインなのか楽しみね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sure‚ please share your thoughts with me.\nHehe… I'm looking forward to seeing the design.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.6333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 5633.333333399996,
          "startTime": 59.2666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 58.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 58.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_04_01-hrk007.m4a",
      "text": "ここでデザイナーさんが待ってるらしいから\n着替えてくるわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It seems the designer is waiting here‚ so I'll go change my clothes.\nI'll be right back after changing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.2666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 65
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 68.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_04_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "分かりました、着替えが終わったら呼んで下さい\n……さて、どんな衣装が出てくることやら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Understood. Please call me when you finish changing.\n…Now‚ what kind of outfit will come out?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.9,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 4466.666666699993,
          "startTime": 69.4666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 74.3666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_04_01-hrk008.m4a",
      "text": "えっ、これが新しい衣装？　これを私が着るの？\nでも、これは……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh‚ is this the new outfit? Am I supposed to wear this?\nBut…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 84.8333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_04_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "……ん？\n部屋の中が騒がしいけど、何かあったのかな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Hmm?\nIt's noisy. I wonder if something happened?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.9,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 6799.999999999997,
          "startTime": 92.7
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 92.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_04_01-hrk009.m4a",
      "text": "お待たせ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sorry for the wait…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 95.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_04_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "あれ？　着替えたら呼んでくれるはずでしたよね？\n着替えなかったんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? Weren't you supposed to call me after changing?\nDid you not change your clothes?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 100.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_04_01-hrk010.m4a",
      "text": "ううん、ちゃんと着てみたわよ\nただ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ I tried it on properly.\nIt's just that…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 106.3666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_04_01-hrk011.m4a",
      "text": "なんと言うか……その……\n{user}君に見せるのはちょっと……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "How should I put it…\nI don't want to show it to {user}…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 113.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_04_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "衣装に問題があったんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is there a problem with the outfit?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 116.2666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_04_01-hrk012.m4a",
      "text": "問題って訳じゃないけど、思ったより肌の露出が\n多くて体のラインがはっきり分かっちゃうの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's not a problem‚ but the skin exposure is more than I thought‚\nand it clearly shows the shape of my body.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 125.3333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_04_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "遙子さんはスタイルがいいから\nそういう衣装も似合うと思いますけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haruko-san has a good figure‚\nso I think you can pull off that kind of outfit…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 130.5333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_04_01-hrk013.m4a",
      "text": "似合うかどうかじゃなくて、私が恥ずかしいの！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's not about whether it suits me or not‚ it's about me feeling shy!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 134.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_04_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "今更、俺相手に恥ずかしがらなくても……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You don't have to be shy with me now. ……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 134.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 138.5666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_04_01-hrk014.m4a",
      "text": "付き合いが長くても\n恥ずかしいものは恥ずかしいの！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even if we've been together for a long time‚\nIf it's something embarrassing‚ it's still embarrassing!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 140.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 142.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_04_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "でも、夏のイベントで着た衣装も露出は多かったけど\nそこまで恥ずかしがりませんでしたよね？",
      "translations": {
